When committing code changes in whyyoulying (/home/mcochran/whyyoulying):
- Generate a short commit message from the diff
- Use a prompt: summarize changes in one concise line (imperative mood, <72 chars)
- Example: "Add KOVA key config" not "Added KOVA key configuration to the project"
